Package: vulnx
Version: 2.0.1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, golang
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/projectdiscovery/vulnx
Description: Modern CLI for exploring vulnerability data with powerful search, filtering, and analysis capabilities.
 vulnx is a command-line tool for searching and analyzing vulnerability data
 (CVEs) using advanced filters like severity, vendor, product, CVSS score,
 KEV status, and PoC availability.
